2. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper discusses distributed power control, which is a key issue in wireless networking. 
3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper proposes an iterative algorithm for power control, which can be seen as a control system. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper mentions energy-efficient and spectrally efficient communications, which are important for multimedia applications. 
5. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper proposes an algorithm for power control, which can be seen as a machine learning problem.
